set up in honor of fechter after his aug 17 1962 death 
fechter bled for nearly an hour before his body was hauled away 
here where peter fechter died we can feel how much suffering 
the wall caused said the east berlin mayor 
a weathered photograph of the young man lying in agony is tacked 
to the cross dark wood more than a dozen large flower 
arrangements were placed by the cross 
although the wall has disappeared there windows on the eastern 
side still have the bars that kept people from jumping to freedom 
from nearby buildings 
in years past the communist east germans marked the walls 
anniversary with bombastic military parades that drew the wrath of 
the western allies 
more than 25 million east germans fled to the west from 1949 
until the wall went up 
communist border soldiers killed more than 200 people attempting 
to flee from east berlin or other parts of east germany to the west 
