crossed on foot through rebel lines into governmentcontrolled 
territory in the center of monrovia 
besides goldsmith those detained were michael roddy of reuters 
and mark huband a freelance writer for united press international 
and the guardian of london 
soldiers seized watches wallets and other valuables from the 
journalists some of the items were later returned by senior 
officers but others vanished 
