walk shoeless to the presidential mansion on the way they were 
slapped punched and threatened with rifle butts 
senior officers of president samuel does army later apologized 
for the troops behavior 
you have to understand theyre very nervous said lt col 
moses thomas the journalists later made their way back across 
rebel lines without incident 
