the next month the moribund campus coalition against bigotry 
regrouped and staged an antiracist protest 
black students react with puzzlement and dismay that the bad old 
days may be coming back 
to me it was kind of funny said brian coe a 21yearold 
senior planning to teach special education but he was disappointed 
it gained official status i thought if they can let something 
like that form whats next 
up north the city of brotherly love didnt do it for michael 
spletzer 
