between career and family he and his wife now have six children 
including 7yearold twins he tries to take them all along 
wherever he works 
we had to suspend that because of the air america 
location he said 
i didnt want to risk going through all that business of 
inoculations and kids in the jungle and talk about the snakes 
geography and time permitting they go to school wherever we 
are theres a sense of semipermanence about their education but 
theyre getting one cultural shock they get a cultural 
smorgasbord and that cant be bad 
its rounded and educational for everyone 
the gibsons now have a base here but their principal home 
remains an australian cattle ranch mel wants it known that he is 
no mere gentleman rancher 
its all happening there genetics embryo transfers 
cryogenic tanks with liquid oxygen embryos shipped from above the 
