said then theres the genetic part at the end what you end up 
with walking around on the ground a cow with a sheeps head no 
not really its not genetic engineering 
theyre really nice animals you can practically map out what 
you want and be sure of hitting fairly near the mark you can do in 
three years what took your grandfather all his life 
