<TEXT>
john hiatt is basically a sentimental kind of 
fellow though youd never guess from those dust bowl eyes 5 
oclock shadow and paisley tie 
but talk about rock n roll heroes elvis presley or bob dylan 
and hiatt gets a little mistyeyed a little nostalgic isnt 
