hiatt is from indiana and that means the heartland with all 
the corny talk of family and the outdoors dont expect him to run 
for office but this is one rocker with plenty to say about the 
wife and kids and the music that sprang from this fair land of 
ours 
yeah you surprise yourself when you find out how really 
