<TEXT>
an angry state casino control 
commission on monday ordered donald trump to release information on 
a restructuring that puts the developers three atlantic city 
casinos up as collateral 
however the commission delayed its order for 24 hours to allow 
trumps attorneys to appeal the decision 
the panel ordered all the documents unsealed after trumps 
attorneys asked for a blanket order sealing the more than 1000 
pages of documents detailing a 65 million emergency loan for trump 
the loan was arranged in june after trump missed a date to make 
a payment on bonds sold to finance trump castle casino resort by 
the bay trump made the payment within a 10day grace period after 
receiving a bridge loan while paperwork on the 65 million deal was 
finished 
under the agreement trump for the first time is using his 
casinos as collateral for financial assistance the agreement with 
the banks will restructure about 1 billion of his 13 billion 
casino debt and 19 billion in other debts 
the commission is scheduled to review the bailout on thursday 
and members say they want the plans underpinnings available to the 
public attorneys nicholas ribis and joseph fusco said the 
sensitivity of the documents could jeopardize the negotiations 
acting commission chairwoman valerie armstrong said in a 
scathing opinion that trumps attorneys again failed to prove why 
the public should not know the details of trumps restructuring 
this proposal would if approved by the commission 
collateralize mr trumps ownership of three of the largest casino 
hotels in atlantic city ms armstrong said it is indisputable 
that the economic structure and stability of trumps casino 
holdings in this state is a matter of public concern 
she rejected the argument that details of trumps problems would 
hamper his dealmaking efforts 
it is certainly no secret to the marketplace that mr trump is 
experiencing serious financial difficulties ms armstrong said 
since its april 2 opening the trump taj mahal casino resort has 
hovered around the 13 million a day in gross gaming revenues that 
analysts said it needed to show a profit however those figures 
were achieved in months skewed by the attention given the opening 
and by higher numbers traditionally recorded by the casinos during 
the summer 
trumps other casinos trump castle and trump plaza hotel and 
casino have posted faltering numbers since the taj mahals 
opening 
by a 41 vote the commission rejected attorneys requests to 
seal the documents that included a debt repayment schedule for 
trump which ms armstrong termed the key inquiry of the 
upcoming hearing 
in another development related to trumps restructuring ribis 
said first boston corp would handle the restructuring replacing 
merrill lynch corp which left last week 
